FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Change the number of rows and columns.</summary> <returns>Returns true if this operation succeeded.</returns> <param name="_rows">The number of rows.</param> <param name="_columns">The number of columns.</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Get the sizing option of the specified row.</summary> <returns>The sizing option of the specified row.</returns> <param name="_row">The specified row number.</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Set the sizing option of the specified row.</summary> <param name="_row">The specified row number.</param> <param name="option">The sizing option of the specified row.</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: GetColumnOption
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Get the sizing option of the specified column.</summary> <returns>The sizing option of the specified column.</returns> <param name="_column">The specified column number.</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: SetColumnOption
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Set the sizing option of the specified column.</summary> <param name="_column">The specified column number.</param> <param name="option">The sizing option of the specified column.</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: GetCellPadding
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Get the cell padding. A cell padding is the distance between a table client area and a cell, or between two cells.</summary> <returns>The cell padding.</returns> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: SetCellPadding
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Set the cell padding. A cell padding is the distance between a table client area and a cell, or between two cells.</summary> <param name="value">The cell padding.</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: GetBorderVisible
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Get the border visibility.</summary> <returns>Returns true means the border thickness equals to the cell padding, otherwise zero.</returns> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: SetBorderVisible
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Set the border visibility.</summary> <param name="value">Set to true to let the border thickness equal to the cell padding, otherwise zero.</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: GetCellArea
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Get the cell area in the space of the table's parent composition's client area.</summary> <returns>The cell area.</returns> </Document>
